      • pingAlive

        public void pingAlive(int ID)

        ID - the ID of the device to update

      • getOnlineList

        public java.lang.String getOnlineList()
        WebMethod to get the list of currently online devices. Method also prunes the list of timed out devices before returning the pruned list. Does not perform function if correct password is not included in header of HTTP request.
        Returns:
        the list of online devices

      • getRegisteredPiList

        public java.lang.String getRegisteredPiList()
        WebMethod to get the list of all registered devices. Does not perform function if correct password is not included in header of HTTP request.

        the list of all registered devices in String form
